high_descs: Turn right away from the fridge and then turn right again and walk towards the wooden table
Grab the metal butter knife from the table
Turn left and left again and walk towards the fridge
Open the fridge door and slice the potato on the top shelf
Close the fridge door and open it again
Place the knife inside the fridge on the shelf below the egg
Close and reopen the fridge door
Grab a slice of potato and close the fridge again
Turn left and walk towards the countertop and then towards the microwave at the end of the counter
Open the microwave door and place the potato slice inside. Turn on the microwave and cook the potato slice. Retrieve the potato slice from the microwave
Turn left and walk towards the door, and then turn left again and walk towards the fridge
Open both the fridge and freezer drawer and place the slice of cooked potato by the potato in the fridge. Close the fridge door
anns.task_desc: To slice a potato inside of the fridge, take a slice and cook it, before returning it to the fridge

put the knife in the refrigerator.

grab a slice of potato out of refrigerator.
turn to the left, and left again until microwave on your right,

open refrigerator and put potato slice in it.
